# Simple Accounting — PRD v1

Internal ops app for catalog pricing and early procurement workflow. Ignore the historical “public catalog” framing: **all app screens require login**.

## Actors

- **Guest:** Login page only. No catalog or write access.
- **Admin:** Single seeded account (via `DatabaseSeeder`). Full access to implemented modules after session login. No public registration.

## App shell

- Layout: `AppLayout` — site header + sidebar nav + main panel
- Auth: session login/logout; `/` redirects to `/products`
- Flash feedback: server `Inertia::flash('toast', { type, message })` → Sonner via `FlashToaster`

### Cross-device UX

- **Supported:** tablet (~768px+) and desktop — primary design targets
- Every screen, table, form, modal, and control must remain **visible and fully functional** on tablet and larger
- Phone layouts are best-effort; do not regress tablet/desktop for phone-only tweaks

### Nav modules

| Module | Route | Status |
|--------|-------|--------|
| Products | `/products` | Shipped — search/browse panel (no `purchase_price`) |
| Suppliers | `/suppliers` | Shipped — full CRUD |
| Customers | `/customers` | Shipped — full CRUD |
| Request Quotations | `/request-quotations` | Stub empty panel |
| Purchased Orders | `/purchased-orders` | Stub empty panel |
| Received Orders | `/received-orders` | Stub empty panel |

Admin product management lives under `/admin/products` (also auth-gated).

