## Domain — Product

| Field | Rules |
|-------|--------|
| `name` | Required |
| `description` | Nullable text |
| `quantity` | Integer ≥ 0 |
| `categories` | Many-to-many (`categories` + `category_product`) |
| `purchase_price` | Decimal; **admin-only** — never on `/products` browse props |
| `selling_price` | Decimal; visible on browse + admin |
| `status` | Enum: `available` \| `unavailable` \| `discontinued` |
| Soft delete | `deleted_at`; trashed products hidden from browse panel |

### Products UX

- **Browse (`/products`):** Search by name/description; optional category filter; list shows public fields only (`toPublicArray`)
- **Admin (`/admin/products`):** CRUD + soft delete / restore; category assign; full fields including `purchase_price`
- Soft-deleted products stay out of the browse panel

---

## Domain — Supplier

| Field | Rules |
|-------|--------|
| `name` | Required |
| `contact_name` | Nullable |
| `email` | Nullable, valid email |
| `phone` | Nullable |
| `address` | Nullable text |
| `notes` | Nullable text |
| `status` | Enum: `active` \| `inactive` |
| Soft delete | `deleted_at`; trash filters on index |

### Suppliers UX

- Single index page (`/suppliers`) — **no** dedicated create/edit routes or pages
- Create / edit in a **slide-down modal** on the index
- List: search (`q`), trash filter (`trashed=only|with`), sortable columns (`name`, `contact_name`, `status`)
- Soft delete + restore; toast flash on mutations
- Resource routes: `index`, `store`, `update`, `destroy` + `suppliers.restore` (withTrashed)

