## Out of scope (v1)

Multi-user roles, public registration, public/guest catalog, payments, multi-tenant, mobile API, full RFQ/PO/receiving transaction ledgers (stubs only until scoped).

## Recommended next (v1.x)

- Implement RFQ → Purchased Orders → Received Orders as real domains
- Link suppliers to products / purchase flow
- Product polish: margin, low-stock, price history, admin filters
- Policies/gates even with one admin
- Pagination/empty-state polish across modules
